#: ../../using.rst:338
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Mount Tray` graphical application is used to facilitate the "
"mounting and unmounting of internal disks, USB storage devices, optical "
"media, and network shares. It is included in the system tray by default. If "
"the icon is removed from the system tray, it can be re-added by typing "
